summary: A small player house overlooking Darkwater Pass.
descriptionHtml:
This is an old Norkic Ruin high above Darkwater Pass. Contains enchanting and alchemy tables, display cases, weapon racks, cooking area and lots of containers. It also has an outside blacksmithing area, everything but a smelter. Be warned it is protected by some very tough bandits. May clash with other homes such as Darkwater Home, but i think thats below mine, Darkwater Keep, Darkwater Overlook.....

The update files contains small changes such as a fix for the blacksmithing trough, changed some containers, chest for potions now looks like various bottles on a shelf, crate of scrolls and tomes, etc...see pics....
author: negativespace
